OL,3,C'Crisis' in Welsh schools over levels
OL,4,Cof violence and abuse at teachers
OL,6,FTeachers in Wales who are experiencing
OL,7,Fhigh levels of violence and verbal
OL,8,Fabuse at work "feel abandoned",
OL,9,Faccording to teachers' union NASUWT.
OL,11,FThe union called on the Welsh
OL,12,FGovernment to do more to protect
OL,13,Fteachers and pupils from violent and
OL,14,Fabusive pupil behaviour.
OL,16,FIt comes after the NASUWT's Behaviour
OL,17,Fin Schools survey, carried out in
OL,18,FSeptember 2023, revealed the depth of
OL,19,Fthe problem in Wales. In the last 12
OL,20,Fmonths:
