OL,3,C'Crisis' in Welsh schools over levels
OL,4,Cof violence and abuse at teachers
OL,6,F"Tackling these issues requires
OL,7,Fopenness, transparency and honesty
OL,8,Fabout the scale of the behaviour
OL,9,Fcrisis.
OL,11,F"An all-Wales behaviour summit would,
OL,12,Fin our view, help to highlight the
OL,13,Fissues and develop a programme of
OL,14,Fsolutions that will deliver the
OL,15,Fchanges needed."
OL,17,FNeil Butler, NASUWT national official
OL,18,Ffor Wales, said: "Many have chosen to
OL,19,Fleave the profession and we cannot
OL,20,Frecruit to replace them.
