OL,3,C'Crisis' in Welsh schools over levels
OL,4,Cof violence and abuse at teachers
OL,6,F"The Welsh Government must open its
OL,7,Feyes to the crisis unfolding in our
OL,8,Fschools.
OL,10,F"As a matter of urgency, we need
OL,11,Ffunding for alternative provision and
OL,12,Fincreased classroom support.
OL,14,F"Teachers should be empowered to deal
OL,15,Fwith challenging behaviour through
OL,16,Fdecreased class sizes and balanced
OL,17,Fworkloads.
