OL,3,C'Crisis' in Welsh schools over levels
OL,4,Cof violence and abuse at teachers
OL,6,F"Local councils and senior leaders are
OL,7,Facting as if abusive pupil behaviour
OL,8,Fis not their problem. If we are to
OL,9,Ftackle these issues, we must do it
OL,10,Ftogether ` teachers cannot be expected
OL,11,Fto cope alone."
OL,13,FA Welsh Government spokesperson said:
OL,14,F"Any form of violence or abuse against
OL,15,Fstaff in our schools is completely
OL,16,Funacceptable.
