OL,3,C'Crisis' in Welsh schools over levels
OL,4,Cof violence and abuse at teachers
OL,6,F"We want our schools to be safe and
OL,7,Fwelcoming environments where teachers
OL,8,Fcan get on with their jobs, ensuring
OL,9,Fthat every child and young person is
OL,10,Fsupported to reach their potential.
OL,12,F"There is a duty on local authorities
OL,13,Fand schools to ensure schools are a
OL,14,Fsafe environment for all."
